Title: Example_Beta.rda
Description: The Example_Beta.rda contains a matrix of beta values from three colon adenocarcinoma samples 6285625076_R06C02, 6929718079_R01C01, and 6042316015_R02C02. These samples are from publicly available, data source TCGA at https://portal.gdc.cancer.gov/.
Notes: Zhang Z et al 2022, Farkas SA et al 2013, Zhang W et al 2020, Timp W et al 2014, Lennard K et al 2016

Title: HiTIMED_Library.rda
Description: The HiTIMED_Library.rda contains matrices of the the average DNA methylation values of the probes included in 6 layers of the HiTIMED deconvolution for 20 types of carcinomas.
Notes: Zhang Z et al 2022, Farkas SA et al 2013, Zhang W et al 2020, Timp W et al 2014, Lennard K et al 2016
